Package cop4331.models

Class Item

java.lang.Object
cop4331.models.Item
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Item extends Object implements Serializable
Represents an item available for sale within the system. Implements Serializable to enable serialization of Item objects.
Author:
S Hassan Shaikh, Austin Vasquez, Divyesh Mangapuram, Jorge Martinez
